  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Topic Centre for the Global Land Cover Network (GLCN) ? A Blueprint for Land Cover and Land Cover Dynamics</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Overall development objective of the Topic Centre for the Global Land Cover Network is to facilitate informed multi scale decision-making related to sustainable management of land and water resources, strengthen food security and improve environmental protection through easier accessibility to reliable land cover information products in harmonized formats. The project is the first phase of a multi-phase programme of activities that will focus will beon developing countries and in particular regional centres of excellence in land cover related activities that can foster the principles of GLCN. It is designed to support regional and progressively national facilities , which lack the capacities to fully benefit from recent advances of geo-information technologies, such as satellite remote sensing, geographic information systems and global positioning systems.</narrative>
  </description>
